en.title: FE Welcomes QP Wearer, Legendary Filipino Singer, Freddie Aquilar "Anak"!
en.content:
Freddie Aquilar is the most famous singer/musician of the Philippines. Freddie's song "Anak" became a worldwide hit and was released in 56 countries in more than 26 different languages and sold over 30 million copies!

Photos below show FE's Philippines Country Licensee, Jeremy Looi doing demos with the Quantum Pendant with Freddie and a proud Freddie wearing FE's QP.
